name: Slashed Ace - Degenerate
description:
Degenerate - adj.

- Having declined from an ancestral state
- Having sunk to a lower and usually corrupt and vicious state
- Characterized by atoms stripped of there electrons by very great density


After two weeks of unrelenting gas fees, paying out over a full $ETH to the miners in order to deliver a community project, staying up all night, neglecting my family and responsiblities, I feel I can no longer proceed to bleed. I have spent countless hours of work to feed the mouths of GPU banks, stressing endlessly about whether or not to continue.

I have become a degenerate - I watch as my electrons drift into the ether by the great density of that which I have gotten myself into.

Fuck Ethereum
